---
import Layout from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import coatImage from "../images/coat/coat_akita.jpg";
import castsImage from "../images/casts/casts_pawdogblackstand.jpg";
import skeletonImage from "../images/skeleton/skeleton_skullcrossbonescatfur.jpg";
import taxidermyImage from "../images/taxidermy/taxidermy_dogproudcard.webp";
import LineFancy from "../components/LineFancy.astro";

---

<Layout title="Preservation">
  <div class="px-4 pt-4 font-display text-4xl lg:px-24 lg:text-6xl lg:pt-8 font-bold">
    Preservation
  </div>
  <div class="px-4 pt-4 font-display text-lg lg:px-24 lg:text-2xl lg:pt-4">
    We provide aftercare for the most challenging time in pet companionship.
  </div>
  <div class="justify-left flex items-center pl-4 pt-2 lg:hidden">
    <LineFancy width="40%" />
  </div>
  <div class="justify-left items-center pl-4 pt-2 hidden lg:flex lg:px-24 lg:pt-4">
    <LineFancy width="30%" />
  </div>
  <div class="px-4 pt-2 lg:px-24">
    Just as every individual and family's relationship with their pet is unique,
    so is our approach to understanding and supporting you. There are a number
    of ways you can memorialize your companion.
  </div>
  <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-4 lg:px-24">
    As you'll notice when looking through our past work, families commonly
    combine services to find the best way to memorialize their pet, such as a
    combined skeleton, coat, and cast preservation. All images shown are
    projects that were completed by Precious Creature. They are presented here
    with the express permission of the loved one's family.
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:gap-x-6 justify-items-center px-10 pt-4 lg:px-24">
    <div class="card glass mb-10">
      <figure>
        <Image src={coatImage} alt="Akita's pelt with a focus on the face!" />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <a class="card-title text-3xl">Coat</a>
        <a class="text-sm"
          >Versatile and intimate, the warmth of your pet's coat is a tangible
          memorial to hold.</a
        >
        <div class="card-actions justify-center">
          <a href="/fur"><button class="btn text-lg">Past work</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card glass mb-10">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={castsImage}
          alt="Casts of two large dog paws on a black stand"
        />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <a class="card-title text-3xl">Casts</a>
        <a class="text-sm"
          >Inorganic and lifelike, casts use alternative materials to
          commemorate your beloved.</a
        >
        <div class="card-actions justify-center">
          <a href="/casts"><button class="btn text-lg">Past work</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card glass mb-10">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={skeletonImage}
          alt="Dog's skull with a jar of bones and a plant in the background"
        />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <a class="card-title text-3xl">Skeleton</a>
        <a class="text-sm"
          >Revealing and elegant, bones tell the remarkable story of your loved
          one's life.</a
        >
        <div class="card-actions justify-center">
          <a href="/bones"><button class="btn text-lg">Past work</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card glass lg:mb-10">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={taxidermyImage}
          alt="Taxidermied small dog, sitting up and looking proud"
        />
      </figure>
      <div class="card-body">
        <a class="card-title text-3xl">Taxidermy</a>
        <a class="text-sm"
          >Sculptural and emotive, taxidermy preserves your pet's body to
          cherish forever.</a
        >
        <div class="card-actions justify-center">
          <a href="/full"><button class="btn text-lg">Past work</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script src="../scripts/lightbox.js"></script>
